snippet: Led by Zhang Chenglong on the horizontal bar, host China won its sixth straight gold medal in the men’s team event at the gymnastics world championships in Nanning.
abstract: China wins its sixth straight gold medal in the men's team event at the gymnastics world championships in Nanning.
